Alright, I'm feeling up to it and I want more people to know about it so. I'm gonna be story timing the online webcomic Nefarious.

Nefarious is a webcomic created by Josh Hano that follows the titular villain Crow after the events of the video game Nefarious. For a quick recap, in the game the villain and protagonist Crow decides to put plans for world domination into effect, kidnapping every princess outside of his own jurisdiction. However, when he's at the crusp of victory, his own conscience and friendship with his own Princess, Princess Mayapple, causes him to call off the plan at the last second. After defeating his secretary in an attempted double cross, the two reconcile and decided to bide their time to perform villainy again some other day.

The comic takes place a few months after the game ends (to my recollection) and for the most part can be enjoyed without too much prior context, but for the purposes of new readers I will be providing context when needed.

With that out of the way, let's get started!
